line=379 fonts=F2-10.9 bbox=72.0,703.98,525.65,714.89                   :phrases can be modified by adverbs but not by nominal modifiers and cannot be combined with a plural
line=380 fonts=F2-10.9 iscore=0.28 bbox=72.0,690.48,525.53,701.39       :morpheme  ‘tul’. The internal properties of gerunds as verbs have been discussed in (Chung et al., 2001).
line=381 fonts=F2-10.9 iscore=0.12 bbox=82.92,676.92,525.58,687.83      :  Additional evidence for not treating NGPs as NPs comes from morphosyntactic properties of comple-
